{
    "id": "completionist/v3",
    "title": "Completionist Award III: The Systems Constellation",
    "description": "Build a grand mixed-discipline trophy that fuses fabrication, woodworking, electronics, robotics, and living systems into one artifact.",
    "image": "/assets/quests/completionist_trophy_award.jpg",
    "npc": "/assets/npc/dChat.jpg",
    "start": "start",
    "dialogue": [
        {
            "id": "start",
            "text": "You did it — every v3 quest path is complete. Let's celebrate by building the Completionist Award III: a living systems trophy that proves you can connect all the disciplines into one coherent build.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "print-lattice",
                    "text": "I am ready to build the grand trophy"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "print-lattice",
            "text": "First we print the precision lattice spine: interlocking trusses, cable channels, and mounting rails for later modules.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "print-completionist-iii-lattice",
                    "text": "Print the lattice spine"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "craft-base",
                    "text": "Lattice print is clean and dimensionally accurate",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "0ebe72b8-4332-4268-b453-801f7818845c",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "craft-base",
            "text": "Now craft the wood base from pine. We need flat faces, true corners, and a protected finish so the electronics and planter can mount safely.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "craft-completionist-iii-wood-base",
                    "text": "Cut, sand, and finish the wood base"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "assemble-electronics",
                    "text": "Wood base is level, sealed, and ready for assembly",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "4d349318-f76b-4a44-973b-eb7467d0c6d3",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "assemble-electronics",
            "text": "Build the electronics harness: status LED ring, servo-driven accent vane, and a debug header so future quests can extend the trophy.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-completionist-iii-electronics",
                    "text": "Solder and heat-shrink the harness"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "planter-module",
                    "text": "Electronics harness passes continuity and servo sweep checks",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "ee5e5a35-f17c-4de1-8053-975fd52c2dd9",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "planter-module",
            "text": "Integrate living systems with a compact planter capsule for basil. This marks the award as a growing artifact, not a static object.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "assemble-completionist-iii-planter-module",
                    "text": "Assemble and plant the bio module"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "systems-integration",
                    "text": "Planter module is rooted, watered, and secure",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "93ea99a9-9e21-4032-aec4-a825f77d23af",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "systems-integration",
            "text": "Bring everything together with the displayed Award II as the historical core, then mount the new modules around it.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "integrate-completionist-iii-systems",
                    "text": "Integrate the full trophy stack"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "qa-signoff",
                    "text": "Integrated assembly is structurally stable with clean cable routing",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "a96ea2cb-faca-4acd-95c5-39f853fdce36",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "qa-signoff",
            "text": "Final QA: verify electronics, structural joints, and planter irrigation. This is your capstone acceptance test.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "process",
                    "process": "validate-completionist-iii-award",
                    "text": "Run final validation and sign-off"
                },
                {
                    "type": "goto",
                    "goto": "finish",
                    "text": "All subsystems pass and the award is ready for display",
                    "requiresItems": [
                        {
                            "id": "86b5d4e1-e4f0-40b1-9a5a-e57cbc65640a",
                            "count": 1
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "finish",
            "text": "Completionist Award III is yours. You started with isolated skills and now you are orchestrating whole systems. I cannot wait to see where you take DSPACE next — autonomous habitats, closed-loop cities, or missions we have not even named yet.",
            "options": [
                {
                    "type": "finish",
                    "text": "Accept the Completionist Award III"
                }
            ]
        }
    ],
